{
  "page": "Maegor Targaryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Maegor Targaryen</b> has been the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>, also known as <i>Maegor the Cruel</i>, third Targaryen king</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_Targaryen_(son_of_Aerion)\" title=\"Maegor Targaryen (son of Aerion)\">Maegor Targaryen</a>, only son of Prince Aerion Targaryen and Princess Daenora Targaryen.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_III_Targaryen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maegor III Targaryen\">Maegor III Targaryen</a>, a character created for and mentioned briefly in the fifth season of <i>Game of Thrones</i>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maegor_Targaryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Maegon_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegon Targaryen\">Maegon Targaryen</a>, a Lord of Dragonstone before the Conquest</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maelor_Targaryen\" title=\"Maelor Targaryen\">Maelor Targaryen</a>, younger son of King Aegon II Targaryen and Queen Helaena Targaryen</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183108\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐ex